for dev build
npx parcel <location>

for prod build
npx parcel build <location>

to shorten this process we can use scripts in package.json file
"scripts": {
    "st": "parcel ./common/index.html",
    "start": "parcel index.html",
    "build": "parcel build index.html",
    "test": "jest"
},

after this we can use
npm run start/npm start
npm run build